snippet.title: They came from another planet - game trailer
snippet.description:
A twin stick, fixed shooter, bonus hell, pixel art, shoot 'em up. 

Aliens have invaded and you, a blue housecat with a stretchy head, are, of course, our last hope. Fight the aliens on earth, under the ocean and in space in this risk/reward based fixed shooter inspired by old arcade shoot 'em ups.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1742290/They_came_from_another_planet/
